msgstr "<strong>ມີການອະນຸມັດການເປັນພັນທະມິດກັບສະໂມສອນອື່ນບໍ່?</strong>"

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Audience Segmentation:</strong> Target specific groups—like VIP "
"members or recent joiners—for more personalized outreach."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ການແບ່ງກຸ່ມຜູ້ຊົມ:</strong> ກຳນົດເປົ້າໝາຍສະເພາະກຸ່ມ ເຊັ່ນ ສະມາຊິກ VIP ຫຼື ຜູ້ທີ່ຫາກໍ່ເຂົ້າຮ່ວ"
"ມ ເພື່ອການເຂົ້າເຖິງທີ່ເປັນສ່ວນຕົວຫຼາຍຂຶ້ນ."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Automate Your Renewals</strong><br/>\n"
"                <br/>\n"
"                Set up automatic reminders and renewal workflows in the Subscription app to avoid missed payments and lapses in membership. Combine it with automated email marketing to re-engage members who haven't renewed."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ຕໍ່ອາຍຸແບບອັດຕະໂນມັດ</strong><br/>\n"
"                <br/>\n"
"                ຕັ້ງຄ່າການແຈ້ງເຕືອນ ແລະ ຂັ້ນຕອນການຕໍ່ອາຍຸອັດຕະໂນມັດໃນແອັບ Subscription ເພື່ອ"
"ຫຼີກລ່ຽງການພາດຊຳລະເງິນ ແລະ ການຂາດສະພາບສະມາຊິກ. ໃຊ້ຮ່ວມກັບການຕະຫຼາດຜ່ານອີເມວອັດຕະໂນມັດ ເພື່ອດຶ"
"ງດູດສະມາຊິກທີ່ຍັງບໍ່ທັນຕໍ່ອາຍຸໃຫ້ກັບມາ."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Automated Billing &amp; Invoicing:</strong> Reduce administrative "
"overhead by automating invoicing and payment reminders."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ການຄິດໄລ່ເງິນ ແລະ ອອກບິນອັດຕະໂນມັດ:</strong> ຫຼຸດຜ່ອນວຽກບໍລິຫານດ້ວຍການອອກໃບເກັບເງິ"
"ນ ແລະ ແຈ້ງເຕືອນການຊຳລະເງິນແບບອັດຕະໂນມັດ."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Branded Products:</strong> Offer branded items like t-shirts, mugs, "
"or event tickets in your online shop."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ສິນຄ້າຂອງສະໂມສອນ:</strong> ຂາຍສິນຄ້າທີ່ມີໂລໂກ້ ເຊັ່ນ ເສື້ອຢືດ, ຈອກ ຫຼື ບັດເຂົ້າຮ່ວມກິດຈະກ"
"ຳໃນຮ້ານຄ້າອອນລາຍຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Bundle Memberships with Exclusive Products or Events</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>ຂາຍຊຸດສະມາຊິກພ້ອມກັບສິນຄ້າພິເສດ ຫຼື ກິດຈະກຳຕ່າງໆ</strong>"

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>CRM Integration:</strong> Capture new leads directly from event "
"sign-ups and follow up post-event."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ການເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ CRM:</strong> ເກັບກຳລາຍຊື່ຜູ້ສົນໃຈໃໝ່ໂດຍກົງຈາກການລົງທະບຽນກິດຈະກຳ ແລະ ຕິ"
"ດຕາມຜົນຫຼັງຈົບງານ."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.homepage
msgid "<strong>Can you trust our community partners?</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>ທ່ານສາມາດໄວ້ວາງໃຈພັນທະມິດຊຸມຊົນຂອງພວກເຮົາໄດ້ບໍ່?</strong>"

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Churn Reduction:</strong> Use metrics and automatic follow-ups to "
"reduce cancellations and boost renewals."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ຫຼຸດຜ່ອນການຍົກເລີກ:</strong> ໃຊ້ຕົວຊີ້ວັດ ແລະ ການຕິດຕາມອັດຕະໂນມັດ ເພື່ອຫຼຸດຜ່ອນການຍົກເລີ"
"ກ ແລະ ເພີ່ມການຕໍ່ອາຍຸສະມາຊິກ."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Coupons &amp; Promotions:</strong> Launch exclusive offers and "
"campaigns to drive traffic and sales."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ຄູປອງ ແລະ ໂປຣໂມຊັ່ນ:</strong> ອອກຂໍ້ສະເໜີພິເສດ ແລະ ແຄມເປນຕ່າງໆ ເພື່ອເພີ່ມການເຂົ້າຊົ"
"ມ ແລະ ຍອດຂາຍ."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Email Campaigns:</strong> Announce new events, welcome new members, "
"or send newsletters with beautifully designed emails."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ແຄມເປນອີເມວ:</strong> ປະກາດກິດຈະກຳໃໝ່, ຕ້ອນຮັບສະມາຊິກໃໝ່ ຫຼື ສົ່ງຂ່າວສານດ້ວຍອີເມວທີ່ອ"
"ອກແບບມາຢ່າງສວຍງາມ."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Event Management:</strong> Plan and manage seminars, galas, "
"tournaments, or online webinars with ease."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ການຈັດການກິດຈະກຳ:</strong> ວາງແຜນ ແລະ ຈັດການສຳມະນາ, ງານລ້ຽງ, ການແຂ່ງຂັນ ຫຼື ເ"
"ວບິນາອອນລາຍໄດ້ຢ່າງງ່າຍດາຍ."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Event Pages:</strong> Automatically create sleek event pages with "
"schedules, speaker bios, and registration forms."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ໜ້າກິດຈະກຳ:</strong> ສ້າງໜ້າກິດຈະກຳທີ່ທັນສະໄໝແບບອັດຕະໂນມັດ ພ້ອມຕາຕະລາງ, ປະຫວັດຜູ້ບັນ"
"ຍາຍ ແລະ ແບບຟອມລົງທະບຽນ."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Flexible Plans:</strong> Create different subscription "
"models—monthly, annual, family, student, etc."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ແຜນການທີ່ຢືດຢຸ່ນ:</strong> ສ້າງຮູບແບບການສະໝັກທີ່ຫຼາກຫຼາຍ ເຊັ່ນ ລາຍເດືອນ, ລາຍປີ, ແບບຄອ"
"ບຄົວ, ນັກຮຽນ ແລະ ອື່ນໆ."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Follow-Ups and Reminders:</strong> Automate communications for "
"membership expirations, event invitations, and special announcements to keep"
" your community engaged."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ການຕິດຕາມ ແລະ ແຈ້ງເຕືອນ:</strong> ສື່ສານແບບອັດຕະໂນມັດສຳລັບການໝົດອາຍຸສະມາຊິກ, ຄຳເ"
"ຊີນຮ່ວມງານ ແລະ ການປະກາດພິເສດ ເພື່ອຮັກສາການມີສ່ວນຮ່ວມຂອງຊຸມຊົນ."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:event.event,description:members_club.event_event_1
msgid "<strong>Free for members | Guests €30</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>ຟຣີສຳລັບສະມາຊິກ | ແຂກທົ່ວໄປ €30</strong>"

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.homepage
msgid "<strong>How is your privacy protected?</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>ຄວາມເປັນສ່ວນຕົວຂອງທ່ານຖືກປົກປ້ອງແນວໃດ?</strong>"

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Integrated Contact Forms:</strong> Connect your forms directly to "
"your CRM pipeline to follow up with interest."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ແບບຟອມຕິດຕໍ່ແບບເຊື່ອມໂຍງ:</strong> ເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ແບບຟອມຂອງທ່ານໂດຍກົງກັບລະບົບ CRM ເພື່ອຕິດຕ"
"າມຜູ້ທີ່ສົນໃຈ."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.homepage
msgid "<strong>Is the membership process straightforward?</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>ຂັ້ນຕອນການສະໝັກສະມາຊິກງ່າຍດາຍບໍ່?</strong>"

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Lead Management:</strong> Track incoming requests, categorize "
"potential members, and nurture them through a personalized onboarding "
"journey."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ການຈັດການຜູ້ສົນໃຈ:</strong> ຕິດຕາມຄຳຮ້ອງຂໍ, ແບ່ງປະເພດຜູ້ທີ່ອາດເປັນສະມາຊິກ ແລະ ເບິ່ງແຍ"
"ງພວກເຂົາຜ່ານຂັ້ນຕອນການເລີ່ມຕົ້ນທີ່ເປັນສ່ວນຕົວ."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Marketing Automation:</strong> Trigger actions based on user "
"behavior—for example, follow up with visitors who abandon their subscription"
" cart."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ການຕະຫຼາດອັດຕະໂນມັດ:</strong> ກະຕຸ້ນການເຮັດວຽກຕາມພຶດຕິກຳຜູ້ໃຊ້ ເຊັ່ນ ຕິດຕາມລູກຄ້າທີ່ເລືອ"
"ກສະໝັກສະມາຊິກແລ້ວແຕ່ຍັງບໍ່ທັນຊຳລະເງິນ."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Member Portal:</strong> Let members log in to view their "
"subscriptions, past orders, and upcoming events."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ລະບົບສະມາຊິກ:</strong> ໃຫ້ສະມາຊິກເຂົ້າສູ່ລະບົບເພື່ອເບິ່ງລາຍການສະໝັກ, ປະຫວັດການສັ່ງຊື້ ແລ"
"ະ ກິດຈະກຳທີ່ຈະມາເຖິງ."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Membership Database:</strong> Manage your current members in one "
"place—view statuses, membership levels, renewal dates, and more."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ຖານຂໍ້ມູນສະມາຊິກ:</strong> ຈັດການສະມາຊິກທັງໝົດໃນບ່ອນດຽວ ເບິ່ງສະຖານະ, ລະດັບສະມາຊິ"
"ກ, ວັນທີຕໍ່ອາຍຸ ແລະ ອື່ນໆ."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Memberships in the Shop:</strong> Sell memberships just like "
"products—visitors can sign up and pay online in minutes."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ຂາຍສະມາຊິກຜ່ານຮ້ານຄ້າ:</strong> ຂາຍການເປັນສະມາຊິກຄືກັບສິນຄ້າ ຜູ້ເຂົ້າຊົມສາມາດສະໝັກ ແລ"
"ະ ຊຳລະເງິນອອນລາຍໄດ້ໃນບໍ່ເທົ່າໃດນາທີ."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:blog.post,content:members_club.blog_post_1
msgid ""
"<strong>Next up:</strong> Stay tuned for our <em>Silent Mornings</em> pilot "
"sessions launching in June—quiet co-working, guided journaling, and "
"intentional starts to the day."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ລຳດັບຖັດໄປ:</strong> ກຽມພົບກັບກິດຈະກຳທົດລອງ <em>Silent Mornings</em> ທີ່ຈະເລີ່ມ"
"ໃນເດືອນມິຖຸນາ—ການເຮັດວຽກໃນຄວາມງຽບ, ການຂຽນບັນທຶກ ແລະ ການເລີ່ມຕົ້ນມື້ໃໝ່ຢ່າງມີສະຕິ."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Opportunities &amp; Upsells:</strong> Identify and follow up on "
"upselling opportunities such as premium memberships or VIP event passes."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ໂອກາດ ແລະ ການຂາຍເພີ່ມ:</strong> ຄົ້ນຫາ ແລະ ຕິດຕາມໂອກາດການຂາຍ ເຊັ່ນ ການອັບເກຣດ"
"ເປັນສະມາຊິກພຣີມຽມ ຫຼື ບັດເຂົ້າງານ VIP."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>SEO &amp; Analytics:</strong> Optimize visibility and track visitor "
"behavior to keep improving."
msgstr ""
"<strong>SEO ແລະ ການວິເຄາະ:</strong> ປັບແຕ່ງໃຫ້ຄົນຄົ້ນຫາເຫັນໄດ້ງ່າຍ ແລະ ຕິດຕາມພຶດຕິກຳຜູ້ເຂົ້າຊົມ"
"ເພື່ອພັດທະນາຢ່າງຕໍ່ເນື່ອງ."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:event.event,description:members_club.event_event_1
msgid "<strong>Schedule</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>ຕາຕະລາງ</strong>"

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Segment Your Community for Better Engagement</strong><br/>\n"
"                <br/>\n"
"                Use tags and filters in the <strong>CRM</strong> and <strong>Email Marketing</strong> apps to segment your members based on interests, membership tier, or activity. This lets you send targeted campaigns and event invitations\n"
"                that feel personal."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ແບ່ງກຸ່ມຊຸມຊົນເພື່ອການມີສ່ວນຮ່ວມທີ່ດີຂຶ້ນ</strong><br/>\n"
"                <br/>\n"
"                ໃຊ້ແທັກ ແລະ ຕົວຕອງໃນແອັບ <strong>CRM</strong> ແລະ <strong>Email "
"Marketing</strong> ເພື່ອແບ່ງກຸ່ມສະມາຊິກຕາມຄວາມສົນໃຈ, ລະດັບສະມາຊິກ ຫຼື ກິດຈະກຳ. ສິ່ງນີ້ຈະຊ່ວຍໃຫ້"
"ທ່ານສົ່ງແຄມເປນ ແລະ ຄຳເຊີນຮ່ວມງານທີ່ກົງຈຸດ ແລະ ເປັນສ່ວນຕົວຫຼາຍຂຶ້ນ."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Self-Service Portal:</strong> Let members manage their own accounts,"
" upgrade plans, or cancel via your website."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ລະບົບບໍລິການຕົນເອງ:</strong> ໃຫ້ສະມາຊິກຈັດການບັນຊີຂອງຕົນເອງ, ອັບເກຣດແຜນ ຫຼື ຍົກເລີກຜ່"
"ານເວັບໄຊຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Social Media Dashboard:</strong> Schedule posts, track engagement, "
"and manage your platforms in one place."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ແຜງຄວບຄຸມໂຊຊຽວມີເດຍ:</strong> ຕັ້ງເວລາໂພສ, ຕິດຕາມການມີສ່ວນຮ່ວມ ແລະ ຈັດການແພລດຟ"
"ອມຕ່າງໆໃນບ່ອນດຽວ."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Ticketing System:</strong> Set up ticket tiers, early bird "
"discounts, and QR-code-based check-ins."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ລະບົບບັດ:</strong> ຕັ້ງລະດັບລາຄາບັດ, ສ່ວນຫຼຸດຊ່ວງທຳອິດ (Early bird) ແລະ ການເຊັກອິນ"
"ດ້ວຍ QR-code."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Tips for success</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>ເຄັດລັບສູ່ຄວາມສຳເລັດ</strong>"

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Track Key Metrics in Real Time</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>ຕິດຕາມຕົວຊີ້ວັດຫຼັກແບບສົດໆ</strong>"

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Use the Sign App for Smooth Onboarding</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>ໃຊ້ແອັບ Sign ເພື່ອການເລີ່ມຕົ້ນສະມາຊິກທີ່ສະດວກ</strong>"

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Website Builder:</strong> Easily build pages for your club’s "
"mission, events, blog, or gallery."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ເຄື່ອງມືສ້າງເວັບໄຊ:</strong> ສ້າງໜ້າເວັບສຳລັບພາລະກິດຂອງສະໂມສອນ, ກິດຈະກຳ, ບລັອກ ຫຼື "
"ຮູບພາບໄດ້ຢ່າງງ່າຍດາຍ."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.homepage
msgid "<strong>What benefits do we provide?</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>ພວກເຮົາໃຫ້ສິດທິປະໂຫຍດອັນໃດແດ່?</strong>"

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.homepage
msgid "<strong>What makes us unique?</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>ອັນໃດທີ່ເຮັດໃຫ້ພວກເຮົາມີຄວາມພິເສດ?</strong>"

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.ir_ui_view_3759
msgid "A year of cultural awakening."
msgstr "ໜຶ່ງປີແຫ່ງການປຸກຈິດສຳນຶກດ້ານວັດທະນະທຳ."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.ir_ui_view_3733
msgid ""
"Advanced solution for enterprises. Cutting-edge features and top-tier "
"support for maximum performance."
msgstr ""
"ທາງເລືອກຂັ້ນສູງສຳລັບອົງກອນຂະໜາດໃຫຍ່. ມີຟີເຈີທີ່ທັນສະໄໝ ແລະ ການຊ່ວຍເຫຼືອລະດັບສູງສຸດເພື່ອປະສິດທິພາບສູງສຸ"
"ດ."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:blog.post,content:members_club.blog_post_1
msgid ""
"After the session, members gathered over herbal tea and small bites in the "
"lounge. What was striking wasn’t just how calm the room felt—it was how open"
" everyone became."
