msgstr "ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດເຮັດໄດ້ໂດຍການອັບເກຣດແພັກເກດຂອງທ່ານໃນສ່ວນ Apps."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Your Odoo Members Club Package helps you streamline your operations by:"
msgstr "ແພັກເກດ Odoo Members Club ຈະຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ການດຳເນີນງານຂອງທ່ານສະດວກຂຶ້ນໂດຍ:"

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:members_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Your club’s website is its digital clubhouse—make it welcoming, functional, "
"and conversion-focused."
msgstr ""
