#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:blog.post,content:members_club.blog_post_1
msgid ""
"“I came because I was curious. I left with a new perspective—and three great"
" book recommendations,” said <strong>Marc T.</strong>, a longtime member."
msgstr ""
"\"ຂ້ອຍມາເພາະຄວາມສົງໄສ ແຕ່ຂ້ອຍກັບໄປພ້ອມກັບມຸມມອງໃໝ່—ແລະໄດ້ຮັບຄຳແນະນຳປຶ້ມດີໆອີກ 3 ຫົວ,\" "
"<strong>Marc T.</strong>, ສະມາຊິກເກົ່າກ່າວ."

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:blog.post,content:members_club.blog_post_1
msgid ""
"“I didn’t expect to feel such a shift after only a few breaths,” said member"
" <strong>Sophie L.</strong>"
msgstr ""
"\"ຂ້ອຍບໍ່ຄິດເລີຍວ່າຈະຮູ້ສຶກເຖິງການປ່ຽນແປງໄດ້ຂະໜາດນີ້ ພຽງແຕ່ການຝຶກຫາຍໃຈບໍ່ເທົ່າໃດຄັ້ງ,\" <strong>"
"Sophie L.</strong> ກ່າວ"

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:blog.post,content:members_club.blog_post_1
msgid ""
"“It was like someone turned the volume down on my brain. I walked out "
"feeling 10 pounds lighter.”"
msgstr ""
"\"ມັນຄືກັບວ່າມີໃຜບາງຄົນມາຫຼຸດສຽງລົບກວນໃນສະໝອງຂອງຂ້ອຍ. ຂ້ອຍຍ່າງອອກມາດ້ວຍຄວາມຮູ້ສຶກທີ່ເບົາສະບາຍຄືກັບ"
"ວ່າຍົກພູເຂົາອອກຈາກເອິກ.\""

#. module: members_club
#: model_terms:blog.post,content:members_club.blog_post_1
msgid ""
"“There was something healing about seeing other people wrestle with the same"
" things I do,” added <strong>Elena M.</strong> “It made me feel less alone.”"
msgstr ""
"\"ມັນຄືການໄດ້ຮັບການຢຽວຍາ ເມື່ອເຫັນວ່າຄົນອື່ນກໍກຳລັງຜະເຊີນກັບບັນຫາຄືກັນກັບຂ້ອຍ,\" <strong>Elena "
"M.</strong> ກ່າວຕື່ມ. \"ມັນເຮັດໃຫ້ຂ້ອຍຮູ້ສຶກວ່າບໍ່ໄດ້ຢູ່ໂຕຄົນດຽວ.\""

